name: Alliance Tournament XXI Script
description: It appears to be a discarded script outlining the play-by-play of what should happen in Alliance Tournament XXI. Showing The Tuskers Co. as the tournament winners alongside some buzzwords and explainers to feature in the show... “Control, Rush, Kite, Kingslayer, Flykillers, Tinkers, a bizarre salad dish featuring the Gallente Dominix and some sort of man being chased by what appears to be a Gurista’s Alligator..?
